{
  "title": "Fiery Crispy Egyptian Lamb Flatbread",
  "description": "A spicy and crispy Egyptian dish featuring lamb and white bread, perfect for a post-workout meal, made in a wok with a braise and shojin-friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
